---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy - SafeCaption">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Refund & Cancellation Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last Updated: January 26, 2025</p>

      <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-8">
        <p class="text-blue-300 font-semibold">7-Day Money Back Guarantee</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-1">We offer a 7-day money-back guarantee for new Pro and Enterprise subscriptions.</p>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">1. Refund Eligibility</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white">Eligible for Refund:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>First-time subscribers within 7 days of initial payment</li>
          <li>Service outage exceeding 24 hours (pro-rated refund)</li>
          <li>Billing errors or duplicate charges</li>
          <li>Account charged after cancellation</li>
          <li>Technical issues preventing service use</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mt-4">Not Eligible for Refund:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>API calls already consumed</li>
          <li>Cancellation after 7 days</li>
          <li>Violation of Terms of Service</li>
          <li>Account suspension for abuse</li>
          <li>Change of mind after the refund period</li>
          <li>Free plan users</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">2. Refund Process</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg text-white mb-3">How to Request a Refund:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Email support@safecaption.com within 7 days</li>
            <li>Include your account email and order ID</li>
            <li>Provide reason for refund request</li>
            <li>Our team will review within 48 hours</li>
            <li>Approved refunds processed in 5-7 business days</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">3. Refund Timeline</h2>
        <table class="w-full border border-gray-700">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="text-left p-3 text-white">Payment Method</th>
              <th class="text-left p-3 text-white">Refund Time</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-3">Credit/Debit Card</td>
              <td class="p-3">5-7 business days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-3">UPI</td>
              <td class="p-3">1-3 business days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-3">Net Banking</td>
              <td class="p-3">7-10 business days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-3">Razorpay Wallet</td>
              <td class="p-3">Instant to 24 hours</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">4. Subscription Cancellation</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white">How to Cancel:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Login to your dashboard</li>
          <li>Go to Billing section</li>
          <li>Click "Cancel Subscription"</li>
          <li>Confirm cancellation</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mt-4">Cancellation Policy:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Cancel anytime, effective at end of billing period</li>
          <li>Access continues until period ends</li>
          <li>No partial month refunds</li>
          <li>API keys remain active until expiry</li>
          <li>Data retained for 30 days after cancellation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">5. Plan Downgrades</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Downgrade takes effect next billing cycle</li>
          <li>No refund for current period</li>
          <li>API limits adjusted immediately</li>
          <li>Excess usage charged at standard rates</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">6. Free Trial</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Free Plan Features:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>100 API calls per month</li>
            <li>No credit card required</li>
            <li>Upgrade anytime</li>
            <li>No time limit</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">7. Special Circumstances</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white">Service Issues:</h3>
        <p>If our service is unavailable for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>&gt;4 hours:</strong> 1-day credit</li>
          <li><strong>&gt;24 hours:</strong> 1-week credit</li>
          <li><strong>&gt;72 hours:</strong> Full month refund</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mt-4">Billing Errors:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Duplicate charges: Full refund of duplicate</li>
          <li>Incorrect amount: Refund of difference</li>
          <li>Unauthorized charge: Full investigation and refund if confirmed</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">8. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>If you're unsatisfied with our refund decision:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Contact escalation@safecaption.com</li>
          <li>Provide transaction details and correspondence</li>
          <li>Management review within 72 hours</li>
          <li>Final decision communicated via email</li>
          <li>Razorpay dispute option available if unresolved</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">9. GST and Taxes</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>GST (18%) included in displayed prices</li>
          <li>GST credit notes issued for refunds</li>
          <li>Invoice adjustments for partial refunds</li>
          <li>Tax documents available in dashboard</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">10. Contact Information</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Refund Support:</p>
          <p>Email: support@safecaption.com</p>
          <p>Response Time: 24-48 hours</p>
          <p>Phone: +91-XX-XXXX-XXXX (Mon-Fri, 9 AM - 6 PM IST)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
          <p class="text-yellow-300 font-semibold">Important:</p>
          <p class="text-sm mt-1">Keep your order ID and payment receipt for faster processing.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8">11. Legal Compliance</h2>
        <p>This refund policy complies with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Consumer Protection Act, 2019 (India)</li>
          <li>Information Technology Act, 2000</li>
          <li>RBI guidelines for digital payments</li>
          <li>Razorpay merchant agreement</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-700">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-center">
        Â© 2025 SafeCaption. All rights reserved. | This policy is legally binding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>